<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="C">C</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=History&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: C"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<ul><li>History does not always repeat itself. Sometimes it just yells, 'Can't you remember anything I told you?' and lets fly with a club.
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/John_W._Campbell" title="John W. Campbell">John W. Campbell</a>, <i>Analog Science Fiction/Fact magazine</i>(1965)</li></ul></li></ul>
<ul><li>History, a distillation of <a href="/wiki/Rumors" title="Rumors">rumor</a>.
